00:01:34.031 --> 00:01:36.695
=The Sun in the Dark=

00:01:36.845 --> 00:01:38.824
=Episode 18=

00:02:12.439 --> 00:02:13.240
Master.

00:02:18.419 --> 00:02:19.099
Xiaoying.

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:23.360
You don't need to say anything.

00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:27.199
I know why the Nine Heavens

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:29.360
treated you like this.

00:02:32.159 --> 00:02:32.879
Don't worry.

00:02:33.719 --> 00:02:34.319
I'm here.

00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:38.560
Let's find a place to heal.

00:02:39.240 --> 00:02:39.639
Come.

00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:42.240
Slowly now.

00:02:47.759 --> 00:02:48.159
Here.

00:02:48.759 --> 00:02:49.199
Come.

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:52.159
Be careful.

00:02:54.159 --> 00:02:54.560
Here.

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:56.400
Sir,

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:57.599
one premium room.

00:02:58.780 --> 00:02:59.979
Why are you two here?

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:01.240
All rooms are occupied.

00:03:01.419 --> 00:03:02.419
Try another inn.

00:03:02.580 --> 00:03:03.340
Out! Get out now!

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:06.419
But your sign clearly shows vacancies.

00:03:07.300 --> 00:03:08.219
That was earlier.

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:09.800
None left now.

00:03:11.759 --> 00:03:13.199
You know full well if rooms exist.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.639
Should I check every room myself?

00:03:17.080 --> 00:03:19.599
Can't you get what I'm saying?

00:03:20.240 --> 00:03:22.680
Everyone, come witness this injustice!

00:03:23.240 --> 00:03:25.599
Bai Xiaoying uses her dark magic

00:03:25.800 --> 00:03:28.479
to threaten us in my place!

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:31.120
Nonsense!

00:03:31.439 --> 00:03:32.759
Let me tell you all the truth.

00:03:33.080 --> 00:03:34.360
Bai Xiaoying

00:03:34.479 --> 00:03:36.120
was born a demon witch!

00:03:36.520 --> 00:03:38.840
Every elder in Su City knows it.

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.759
We've known for decades!

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:42.759
She bullied others when she was young!

00:03:43.159 --> 00:03:44.479
How dare she show her face here?

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:45.439
Disgusting!

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:47.639
Consorting with the Night Clan!

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:48.560
Nothing but filth!

00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:49.800
This man she brought

00:03:49.800 --> 00:03:50.560
is her master

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:52.840
who always protected her crimes!

00:03:53.219 --> 00:03:54.460
Look at his wretched state now!

00:03:54.599 --> 00:03:55.800
That's evil reaping its due!

00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:56.960
Exactly!

00:03:57.280 --> 00:03:58.520
We won't share a place

00:03:58.520 --> 00:03:59.400
with these demons!

00:03:59.699 --> 00:04:01.408
- Out!
- Out!

00:04:01.408 --> 00:04:02.080
- Out!
- Out!

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:02.599
Shut up!

00:04:03.104 --> 00:04:03.744
Get out!

00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:06.240
Ungrateful wretches!

00:04:07.199 --> 00:04:09.439
Immortal Yunya saved countless lives!

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:11.719
And this is how you repay him.

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:13.240
Pathetic!

00:04:13.479 --> 00:04:15.080
Saving us?

00:04:15.919 --> 00:04:18.879
The Nine Heavens protected us!

00:04:18.879 --> 00:04:20.680
The Immortal Lord himself!

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:23.959
He just followed the orders

00:04:24.000 --> 00:04:25.160
and did his duty.

00:04:25.639 --> 00:04:27.360
Now, he's exiled from the immortal sect,

00:04:27.959 --> 00:04:29.480
consorting with this...

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:30.000
Right.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:32.040
This demon witch!

00:04:32.199 --> 00:04:33.759
He's no good thing either!

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:35.040
Get lost!

00:04:35.519 --> 00:04:36.680
- Out!
- Out now!

00:04:36.800 --> 00:04:37.600
Go!

00:04:37.720 --> 00:04:39.000
- Get out of here!
- Out!

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:42.240
(These people
have no idea of the truth,)

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:44.360
(but they spew nonsense here.)

00:04:45.399 --> 00:04:46.800
(Doesn't this infuriate you?)

00:04:48.319 --> 00:04:50.040
(Look at their hideous faces.)

00:04:50.839 --> 00:04:52.519
(Don't you want to tear them apart?)

00:04:53.839 --> 00:04:55.360
(I can make it happen.)

00:04:58.160 --> 00:04:58.680
Xiaoying.

00:05:01.519 --> 00:05:02.319
Xiaoying.

00:05:04.079 --> 00:05:04.819
Xiaoying.

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:07.759
Let's leave.

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:14.319
I won't waste time arguing today.

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:17.439
If I hear more slander
against my master,

00:05:18.208 --> 00:05:19.552
you'll face consequences!

00:05:19.552 --> 00:05:20.192
Enough! Out!

00:05:20.192 --> 00:05:21.408
- Go away!
- Get lost!

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.279
I never expected

00:05:52.199 --> 00:05:53.879
when I became worthless trash,

00:05:55.040 --> 00:05:56.319
only you'd stand by me.

00:06:09.339 --> 00:06:10.139
Forget that.

00:06:11.399 --> 00:06:12.639
Are you feeling warmer now?

00:06:19.319 --> 00:06:22.720
(Every hardship he endures
is for my sake.)

00:06:23.959 --> 00:06:25.199
(When he seized the sword.)

00:06:26.040 --> 00:06:27.000
(This time too.)

00:06:28.399 --> 00:06:29.959
(Whatever the cost,)

00:06:30.839 --> 00:06:31.800
(I'll save him.)

00:06:47.079 --> 00:06:49.399
Bai Xiaoying
has fully succumbed to darkness,

00:06:50.079 --> 00:06:52.740
aiding the Night Clan against us!

00:06:53.079 --> 00:06:54.120
Then we will

00:06:54.759 --> 00:06:56.480
strike first

00:06:56.480 --> 00:06:57.600
and eliminate her

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.600
before she causes more harm!

00:07:01.319 --> 00:07:01.839
My lord,

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:04.920
shouldn't we investigate

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:06.600
why the War God
suddenly turned against us

00:07:06.759 --> 00:07:07.519
before doing that?

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:08.839
My lord,

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:10.240
her words make sense.

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:12.000
We require evidence to kill

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:12.639
the War God.

00:07:12.959 --> 00:07:14.839
Perhaps the War God
has compelling reasons.

00:07:15.319 --> 00:07:17.160
Bai Xiaoying's defection
to the Night Clan

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:18.480
is witnessed by all.

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:19.439
The evidence is solid.

00:07:19.600 --> 00:07:20.680
There's no room for doubt.

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.600
This discussion is over.

00:07:23.620 --> 00:07:26.720
She's left the Snowfall Valley
for the Mortal Realm.

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:30.639
This is our chance
to eradicate the Snowfall Valley.

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:34.720
Everyone,

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:37.720
follow me.

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:56.120
Xiaoying.

00:07:57.160 --> 00:07:59.759
Don't drain your spiritual power
for me anymore.

00:08:02.199 --> 00:08:03.319
How do you feel now?

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:08.079
Now, I have

00:08:08.959 --> 00:08:10.199
less than 30% of my power.

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:13.079
I'm practically useless.

00:08:16.519 --> 00:08:17.319
No.

00:08:17.959 --> 00:08:19.680
At dawn, I'll take you
back to the valley.

00:08:20.360 --> 00:08:21.720
Rest there,

00:08:22.879 --> 00:08:24.399
and you'll recover within days.

00:08:30.240 --> 00:08:31.519
How did you find me?

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.120
You already know

00:08:34.600 --> 00:08:35.600
everything?

00:08:40.159 --> 00:08:42.519
I don't know the full details.

00:08:43.240 --> 00:08:45.559
I received Wanyan's message
in the valley

00:08:45.879 --> 00:08:47.080
and learned of your thing.

00:08:50.559 --> 00:08:51.600
This helped me

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:52.879
locate you.

00:08:58.200 --> 00:08:59.519
You've kept it all this time?

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:01.080
Of course.

00:09:02.940 --> 00:09:04.580
It's the first gift you ever gave me.

00:09:05.159 --> 00:09:06.480
I treasure it dearly.

00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:12.240
So...

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:14.399
what exactly happened to you

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:17.039
in the Nine Heavens?

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:24.960
The past

00:09:25.980 --> 00:09:26.899
isn't worth mentioning.

00:09:28.399 --> 00:09:29.399
From now on,

00:09:30.259 --> 00:09:33.259
I have no ties to the Nine Heavens.

00:09:41.159 --> 00:09:44.320
I can stay by your side forever.

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:49.840
It's time.

00:09:50.519 --> 00:09:51.720
Let's return to the valley.

00:09:54.600 --> 00:09:55.399
Snowfall Valley...

00:09:57.679 --> 00:09:58.240
Oh no.

00:09:58.759 --> 00:10:00.000
They'll attack the valley!

00:10:00.799 --> 00:10:01.480
What?

00:10:43.639 --> 00:10:44.360
Little Stone,

00:10:45.039 --> 00:10:45.919
are you alright?

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:47.519
Can you hear me?

00:10:48.600 --> 00:10:49.399
I'm sorry.

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:51.679
War God.

00:10:52.480 --> 00:10:55.799
I failed to protect
the Snowfall Valley for you.

00:10:56.759 --> 00:10:57.559
Nothing.

00:10:58.200 --> 00:10:59.120
Don't speak.

00:10:59.340 --> 00:11:00.419
Let me heal your wounds.

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.919
Leave me.

00:11:03.039 --> 00:11:06.299
Rourou was captured by a group.

00:11:06.580 --> 00:11:08.419
Hurry.

00:11:10.700 --> 00:11:11.299
Little Stone.

00:11:12.539 --> 00:11:13.299
Little Stone.

00:11:31.340 --> 00:11:31.899
Master.

00:11:33.139 --> 00:11:33.860
Stay here.

00:11:35.620 --> 00:11:36.659
I'll rescue Rourou.

00:11:41.399 --> 00:11:42.200
Xiaoying.

00:11:42.960 --> 00:11:52.736
- Kill her!
- Kill her!

00:11:52.998 --> 00:11:53.568
Kill her!

00:11:53.568 --> 00:11:55.919
She's the follower of Bai Xiaoying,

00:11:55.919 --> 00:11:57.419
the Night Clan witch!

00:11:57.860 --> 00:11:59.500
This is what she deserves!

00:11:59.940 --> 00:12:02.299
- Kill her!
- Kill her!

00:12:02.620 --> 00:12:03.379
Tell us.

00:12:03.620 --> 00:12:05.100
Where's Bai Xiaoying?

00:12:05.860 --> 00:12:07.000
As long as you say it,

00:12:07.700 --> 00:12:08.879
we'll release you.

00:12:09.460 --> 00:12:10.379
In your dreams.

00:12:11.100 --> 00:12:12.259
I'd rather die

00:12:12.460 --> 00:12:13.460
than betray her.

00:12:13.779 --> 00:12:14.220
You...

00:12:14.740 --> 00:12:18.620
- Kill her!
- Kill her!

00:12:19.220 --> 00:12:21.340
Do you know how many villagers here

00:12:21.820 --> 00:12:24.740
lost family to the Night Clan?

00:12:25.340 --> 00:12:26.460
The blood on you

00:12:26.740 --> 00:12:28.659
belongs to those victims!

00:12:29.659 --> 00:12:30.624
- Bring him up!
- Go!

00:12:34.139 --> 00:12:35.899
Are you another
of Bai Xiaoying's followers?

00:12:36.100 --> 00:12:36.620
No!

00:12:36.860 --> 00:12:37.740
I'm not!

00:12:38.539 --> 00:12:40.740
That traitor Bai Xiaoying deceived me!

00:12:40.860 --> 00:12:41.740
I had no choice

00:12:41.980 --> 00:12:43.659
but to join them to survive!

00:12:44.299 --> 00:12:45.419
She betrayed the immortals!

00:12:45.419 --> 00:12:46.419
A despicable wretch!

00:12:46.620 --> 00:12:47.740
She's no War God!

00:12:48.379 --> 00:12:49.740
I want to tear her flesh

00:12:49.740 --> 00:12:50.659
and drink her blood!

00:12:51.460 --> 00:12:51.980
Okay.

00:12:52.659 --> 00:12:53.820
You've awakened.

00:12:54.379 --> 00:12:55.019
Let him go.

00:12:59.259 --> 00:13:00.100
Your turn.

00:13:01.139 --> 00:13:01.820
Speak.

00:13:02.259 --> 00:13:04.139
What kind of person is Bai Xiaoying?

00:13:06.379 --> 00:13:08.620
She's the finest person in this world.

00:13:09.059 --> 00:13:10.299
She sacrificed herself

00:13:10.299 --> 00:13:11.820
to save all of you.

00:13:12.179 --> 00:13:13.220
Talking nonsense!

00:13:13.500 --> 00:13:14.899
Shut your lying mouth!

00:13:15.539 --> 00:13:17.179
One last chance.

00:13:17.620 --> 00:13:18.220
Say it!

00:13:18.419 --> 00:13:20.100
- Say it!
- Say it!

00:13:20.100 --> 00:13:22.460
- Hurry up!
- Confess!

00:13:27.899 --> 00:13:29.019
You all witnessed it.

00:13:29.419 --> 00:13:31.139
Still defiant when death approaches.

00:13:31.580 --> 00:13:33.779
Truly bewitched by that demonic woman.

00:13:33.779 --> 00:13:35.620
- Kill her!
- Kill her!

00:13:35.620 --> 00:13:36.820
You deserve your death!

00:13:38.080 --> 00:13:38.816
Kill her!

00:13:40.125 --> 00:13:44.448
- Kill her!
- Kill her!

00:13:53.779 --> 00:13:54.259
You...

00:13:57.340 --> 00:13:57.980
Rourou,

00:13:58.779 --> 00:13:59.580
are you okay?

00:14:00.419 --> 00:14:01.700
Hold on a little longer.

00:14:01.779 --> 00:14:02.620
Xiaoying,

00:14:02.860 --> 00:14:03.740
you came.

00:14:05.179 --> 00:14:05.980
I'm sorry.

00:14:06.940 --> 00:14:09.100
I might not be able to stay with you.

00:14:09.860 --> 00:14:10.580
Rourou.

00:14:11.299 --> 00:14:11.940
Rourou.

00:14:12.500 --> 00:14:13.220
Rourou.

00:14:27.220 --> 00:14:28.100
Rourou.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:31.200
I'm taking you home.

00:14:33.220 --> 00:14:35.860
This is Bai Xiaoying
who killed your families.

00:14:36.220 --> 00:14:38.112
- Stop her!
- Stop her!

00:14:38.899 --> 00:14:40.224
Stop her!

00:14:42.019 --> 00:14:42.779
Witch!

00:14:44.059 --> 00:14:45.059
A life for a life!

00:14:47.633 --> 00:14:49.408
- Kill her!
- Die!

00:14:51.230 --> 00:14:52.302
- Kill her!
- Kill her!

00:14:52.671 --> 00:14:53.568
You die!

00:14:54.879 --> 00:14:55.424
Witch!

00:14:59.419 --> 00:15:00.460
Witch?

00:15:01.740 --> 00:15:04.220
Let me show you a real witch.

00:15:14.299 --> 00:15:14.912
Run!

00:15:24.620 --> 00:15:25.419
What?

00:15:25.620 --> 00:15:27.860
Don't you recognize me?

00:15:28.519 --> 00:15:29.879
Feng Changgeng.

00:15:32.580 --> 00:15:33.820
These refugees

00:15:34.340 --> 00:15:36.379
are truly courting death.

00:15:37.820 --> 00:15:39.100
But blame yourself

00:15:39.980 --> 00:15:41.659
if you must.

00:15:42.460 --> 00:15:44.419
1,500 years have passed.

00:15:44.500 --> 00:15:46.539
You're just a vessel.

00:15:47.059 --> 00:15:48.820
An imprisoned vessel.

00:15:50.740 --> 00:15:52.139
Over these 15 centuries,

00:15:52.899 --> 00:15:54.860
without the sacrifices
of me and Ye Chenyuan,

00:15:55.259 --> 00:15:57.340
the Three Realms
would've perished long ago!

00:15:58.460 --> 00:15:59.700
All your suffering

00:16:00.179 --> 00:16:03.179
was orchestrated by your own mother.

00:16:03.419 --> 00:16:05.740
Even your birth mother
saw you as a tool.

00:16:05.899 --> 00:16:08.620
Your joys, sorrows and desires.

00:16:08.820 --> 00:16:11.340
No one truly cares.

00:16:12.940 --> 00:16:13.580
That's not true.

00:16:15.139 --> 00:16:16.299
I still have Ye Chenyuan.

00:16:19.340 --> 00:16:20.659
Ye Chenyuan.

00:16:21.539 --> 00:16:23.500
Ye Chenyuan grew weary

00:16:23.500 --> 00:16:25.659
of this three-century cycle with you.

00:16:25.980 --> 00:16:27.820
He'd rather end himself

00:16:28.139 --> 00:16:30.740
than remain bound to you.

00:16:31.100 --> 00:16:32.059
It wasn't like that.

00:16:32.700 --> 00:16:33.740
It wasn't like that.

00:16:34.419 --> 00:16:35.460
You're lying!

00:16:36.100 --> 00:16:38.100
Let me reveal another secret.

00:16:38.740 --> 00:16:42.460
Your parents Xi Wu and Jibai's plan

00:16:42.899 --> 00:16:45.620
wasn't just to seal the Night Deity
with you as a vessel.

00:16:46.100 --> 00:16:47.539
They intended to erase both you

00:16:47.539 --> 00:16:50.259
and the Night Deity.

00:16:51.980 --> 00:16:53.019
What?

00:16:58.220 --> 00:16:59.259
Realms stabilized.

00:16:59.460 --> 00:17:00.379
With my energy.

00:17:01.019 --> 00:17:02.299
Heaven and earth as blades.

00:17:02.539 --> 00:17:04.019
- Seal!
- Seal!

00:17:06.940 --> 00:17:08.980
Immortal Changgeng,

00:17:10.140 --> 00:17:12.099
I thought you were wise.

00:17:12.700 --> 00:17:14.819
Do you really intend
to kill me alongside them?

00:17:15.500 --> 00:17:17.500
You should've vanished long ago.

00:17:18.259 --> 00:17:20.539
As the Sword Master,
I'll personally end you.

00:17:20.980 --> 00:17:22.099
This is my duty

00:17:22.099 --> 00:17:23.819
as a cultivator of the Nine Heavens.

00:17:25.019 --> 00:17:26.420
Nine Heavens?

00:17:27.700 --> 00:17:29.299
You crave fame and glory,

00:17:29.740 --> 00:17:31.819
wanting to be the hero of this world

00:17:31.980 --> 00:17:33.579
to make the immortal sect eternal.

00:17:35.519 --> 00:17:36.819
But don't forget.

00:17:37.339 --> 00:17:39.099
For every night, there's dawn.

00:17:39.180 --> 00:17:40.980
For darkness, light exists.

00:17:41.500 --> 00:17:42.700
Killing me

00:17:43.099 --> 00:17:45.579
will only earn fleeting praise.

00:17:45.900 --> 00:17:48.140
To make the Three Realms
depend on the immortal sect

00:17:48.180 --> 00:17:49.940
and worship you eternally,

00:17:50.220 --> 00:17:51.380
Immortal Changgeng,

00:17:52.619 --> 00:17:54.019
