00:17:58.539 --> 00:17:59.339
I know

00:17:59.700 --> 00:18:01.819
you're an intelligent man.

00:18:03.059 --> 00:18:03.980
How about

00:18:04.500 --> 00:18:06.339
we make a deal?

00:18:12.099 --> 00:18:12.779
Changgeng,

00:18:13.856 --> 00:18:15.576
Xi Wu has transformed
into the Divine Sword.

00:18:16.220 --> 00:18:17.619
I will become its spirit.

00:18:19.779 --> 00:18:21.059
You must personally

00:18:22.299 --> 00:18:23.460
kill the Night Deity.

00:18:36.059 --> 00:18:37.019
Changgeng,

00:18:37.740 --> 00:18:38.700
