00:18:40.900 --> 00:18:41.980
Without a sword spirit,

00:18:42.579 --> 00:18:44.660
I can still kill the Night Deity,

00:18:45.220 --> 00:18:48.500
but he will resurrect
alongside the dead baby

00:18:48.940 --> 00:18:50.900
three centuries later.

00:18:51.259 --> 00:18:52.420
When that happens,

00:18:52.700 --> 00:18:55.779
I'll eliminate him again
with the spiritless Divine Sword.

00:18:56.900 --> 00:18:58.500
This cycle will repeat endlessly.

00:18:58.740 --> 00:19:01.099
The Night Deity revives every 300 years,

00:19:01.700 --> 00:19:03.099
making all mortals

00:19:03.740 --> 00:19:05.660
perpetually fear him,

00:19:06.299 --> 00:19:08.220
need our immortal sect,

00:19:09.220 --> 00:19:11.380
and worship

00:19:11.779 --> 00:19:16.380
the Nine Heavens ruled by me.

00:19:39.819 --> 00:19:41.259
Jibai, you wretch!

00:19:41.980 --> 00:19:43.579
Severely wounding me,

00:19:43.940 --> 00:19:47.180
leaving me unable
to wield the Divine Sword.

00:19:52.259 --> 00:19:54.819
