00:21:20.140 --> 00:21:20.940
So...

00:21:21.980 --> 00:21:23.380
So, this is the truth.

00:21:24.900 --> 00:21:30.259
All my endurance meant nothing.

00:21:32.339 --> 00:21:35.299
My life's been a joke.

00:21:37.400 --> 00:21:38.519
Those I loved

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:42.400
and wished to protect

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:46.279
all died because of me.

00:21:47.640 --> 00:21:49.759
The world has abandoned me.

00:21:57.279 --> 00:21:59.279
If the world needs me not,

00:22:01.839 --> 00:22:03.480
why should I need it?

00:22:04.440 --> 00:22:06.400
After coexisting
with the Night Deity so long,

00:22:06.640 --> 00:22:08.319
have you considered,

00:22:08.559 --> 00:22:09.359
Bai Xiaoying,

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:12.200
you are the Night Deity?

00:22:15.799 --> 00:22:17.400
I am the Night Deity.

00:22:21.920 --> 00:22:24.079
This world's beyond saving.

00:22:25.160 --> 00:22:27.720
If salvation is impossible,

00:22:31.279 --> 00:22:33.119
let us all perish together.

00:22:41.980 --> 00:22:44.420
The Night Deity descends!

00:22:50.099 --> 00:22:50.819
Rourou,

00:22:54.740 --> 00:22:56.380
I'll make the entire world

00:22:57.259 --> 00:22:58.700
your funeral offering.

00:23:05.180 --> 00:23:06.059
The Night Deity.

00:23:08.859 --> 00:23:10.180
Now, Xiaoying

00:23:10.539 --> 00:23:11.619
will only go to two places.

00:23:24.099 --> 00:23:25.140
My lord.

00:23:26.900 --> 00:23:28.579
Having left the Nine Heavens for days,

00:23:29.059 --> 00:23:30.700
I finally understand your dedication.

00:23:31.700 --> 00:23:32.740
I've deeply reflected.

00:23:33.940 --> 00:23:35.339
I'm sorry for my past immaturity.

00:23:36.500 --> 00:23:38.500
Grant me another chance

00:23:39.099 --> 00:23:40.099
