00:24:00.700 --> 00:24:02.819
You refused to submit or apologize

00:24:02.900 --> 00:24:05.500
before all the elders
and upper immortals,

00:24:05.660 --> 00:24:08.339
publicly humiliating me.

00:24:10.180 --> 00:24:11.059
I know.

00:24:12.059 --> 00:24:13.539
You rule the Nine Heavens.

00:24:14.180 --> 00:24:15.980
I continued to err without repentance.

00:24:17.019 --> 00:24:18.299
How could you show favoritism?

00:24:33.460 --> 00:24:34.819
Do you know?

00:24:35.740 --> 00:24:39.140
Though Bai Xiaoying
became the Sword Master,

00:24:39.700 --> 00:24:41.420
in my judgment,

00:24:41.460 --> 00:24:44.220
the most qualified candidate

00:24:44.819 --> 00:24:46.220
remains you.

00:24:47.859 --> 00:24:48.660
Yunya,

00:24:49.019 --> 00:24:50.779
