00:24:51.740 --> 00:24:54.660
I'll treat you as before.

00:24:55.059 --> 00:24:56.099
From this day onward,

00:24:56.700 --> 00:24:59.819
you'll be the Sword Master.

00:25:02.660 --> 00:25:04.900
Thank you, my lord.

00:25:20.779 --> 00:25:21.420
Bai Xiaoying.

00:25:22.140 --> 00:25:22.839
What are you...?

00:25:23.700 --> 00:25:24.500
Exactly.

00:25:25.980 --> 00:25:27.619
I'm now the Night Deity.

00:25:29.660 --> 00:25:30.980
Starting today,

00:25:31.819 --> 00:25:34.259
I'll restore the Night Clan's glory.

00:25:34.940 --> 00:25:37.140
Though you helped us before,

00:25:37.740 --> 00:25:38.940
